description:
Danny touches on part 1 of the Real Housewives of Orange County reunion's shocking end, then recaps this week's Real Housewives of Salt Lake City episode, which featured the start of the Vegas trip. Then, we talk Real Housewives of Dallas' Kary's 50th! PLUS: Clare & Dale call it quits! WWHL! JLo!!


RHOC: 5:35ish

RHOSLC: 10:33ish

RHOD: 30:05ish
